View Data in a Dashboard
A dashboard tells you a specific, focused story about data by using a curated set of lenses and widgets.

You can tap charts, buttons, and other elements to dynamically filter and drill into data.
Directly under Account Region, tap All, and then select AMER. The data in the dashboard is instantly updated to represent the North American region.

Filter Your Data
Apply global filters in a dashboard to focus on the subset of data that’s most relevant for your business unit, project, or management team.

Return to the Initial View
To go back to the dashboard’s original state, you can use the reset option to quickly return to the initial view.

View Data in a Lens
You can explore the chart in a lens. Tap  Deselect to explore all of the data in the lens.
Tap  Details to see a table of data about the escalated cases.
Tap  Drill In to chart information about the escalated cases.
